'''Kishor Shantabai Kale''' (1970–2007) was a [[Marathi people|Marathi]] writer and social worker from [[Maharashtra]], [[India]]. He was the son of a [[Kolhati]] [[tamasha]] artist. He studied at the [[Grant Medical College and Sir Jamshedjee Jeejeebhoy Group of Hospitals|Grant Medical College]] to become a medical doctor. Kale died at age 37 in a car accident on February 21, 2007.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://zeenews.india.com/home/noted-marathi-writer-kale-passes-away_355613.html|title=Noted Marathi writer Kale passes away|date=2007-02-21|newspaper=Zee News|access-date=2016-12-19}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{cite web |title=A life lived for the community |url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/a-life-lived-for-the-community/24877/ |publisher=[[Indian Express]] |accessdate=2009-07-26}} Provides a more detailed life sketch of Kale.</ref> He was closely related to Madhu Kambikar an Indian film artist.<ref name=":0" />

== Kolhatyacha por ==
In 1994, he wrote his autobiography ''Kolhatyacha Por'' (son of a kolhati)  (कोल्ह्याट्याचा पोर) in Marathi.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.lokmat.com/storypage.php?catid=1&newsid=16548211|title=‘कोल्हाट्याचं पोर’ची आई मदतीसाठी फिरतेय दारोदारी !|last=|first=|date=|work=|newspaper=Lokmat|access-date=2016-12-19|via=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.in/books?id=b2jYAAAAIAAJ&q=kolhatyacha+por&dq=kolhatyacha+por&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjs1f66_v_QAhVJOo8KHWJwBQoQ6AEIGTAA|title=Documentation on Women & Violence|publisher=Streevani|language=en}}</ref> It has been translated to English by Sandhya Pandey and titled ''Against all odds''.<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Deshmukh|first=Suresh|year=2015|title=Against All Odds : The Unknown World of the Subaltern|url=http://www.epitomejournals.com/VolumeArticles/FullTextPDF/46_Research_Paper.pdf|journal=Epitome Journals|volume=I|pages=|via=}}</ref> There has been a demand from the Kolhati community that the book be banned as they consider it libellous.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.loksatta.com/maharashtra-news/again-demand-for-the-ban-on-kolhatyache-por-157063/lite/|title=‘कोल्हाटय़ाचं पोर’वर बंदीची पुन्हा मागणी – Loksatta|website=www.loksatta.com|access-date=2016-12-19}}</ref>

