'''Manda''', or '''Manda-Matumba''', is a [[Bantu language]] of [[Tanzania]]. It was assigned to the Bena–Kinga (G60) group by Nurse (1988), though Ehret retains it in N10 [[Rufiji–Ruvuma]] (Songea).
